Why are you here today?

281
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:47,470
I just parked here.

282
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:49,670
I called Hongda earlier, but no one answered.

283
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:51,710
I thought he might be at home.

284
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:52,920
He's working overtime.

285
00:14:54,130 --> 00:14:56,560
If you're not busy, why don't you come up for a bit?

286
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:57,990
I'd better not come up then.

287
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,270
Don't say that.

288
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:00,510
I'm making dumplings today.

289
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:01,630
You're in for a treat.

290
00:15:01,740 --> 00:15:03,770
Celery and pork, your favorite.

291
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:05,470
Alright, I'll come up then.

292
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:06,380
Let's go.

293
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:07,720
-Let me carry a bag.
-It’s okay.

294
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:10,040
Have you been busy lately?

295
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:11,090
Yes, busy.

296
00:15:11,430 --> 00:15:12,470
All sorts of things.

297
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:14,470
Otherwise, I wouldn't have been away for so long.

298
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:15,870
Yeah, it's been a while since you've been here.

299
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:16,550
How about Hongda?

300
00:15:16,710 --> 00:15:18,110
Is Hongda also very busy?

301
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,340
He's working overtime every day.

302
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:20,720
But since you're back,

303
00:15:20,990 --> 00:15:22,350
I can give him a call,

304
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,760
taking this chance to ask him to come home.

305
00:15:24,230 --> 00:15:25,630
Starting a business is really not easy.

306
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:27,150
How's Manman doing?

307
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:28,540
She's boarding at school.

308
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:30,030
Aren't you reluctant about that?

309
00:15:30,030 --> 00:15:31,430
What's there to be reluctant about?

310
00:15:32,310 --> 00:15:34,240
I heard from Hongda that Manman is painting

311
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,190
very well now.

312
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:37,510
In his heart,

313
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:39,660
his daughter will always come first.

314
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:44,150
Any pair of shoes will do.

315
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:50,760
I've been busy lately.

316
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:53,190
The house hasn't been tidied up for a while.

317
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,420
It's a mess.

318
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:55,470
Mrs. Zhang,

319
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:56,750
why is everything packed up?

320
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,890
Are you moving?

321
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,110
You have to tell me where you're moving to.

322
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,990
I don't want to end up not knowing where to go for free meals.

323
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:04,910
Don't worry.

324
00:16:04,990 --> 00:16:06,500
Once we're settled,

325
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:08,530
I'll give you a call.

326
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,120
We'll have you over for a housewarming.

327
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:11,990
The place is far,

328
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:13,860
but the landlord has a piece of land.

329
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,270
We can grow some vegetables.

330
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:17,520
Homegrown vegetables just taste different.

331
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:20,190
So you've already found a place?

332
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:23,030
Having some land is nice.

333
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,010
That sounds interesting.

334
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:26,340
But it's so far away.

335
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:28,190
Won't it be too inconvenient?

336
00:16:28,950 --> 00:16:31,190
We'll have to overcome the inconvenience, won't we?

337
00:16:35,230 --> 00:16:37,800
Mrs. Zhang, I heard that

338
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:40,470
Hongda mortgaged the house.

339
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,320
If you're having any difficulties...

340
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,070
Alright, alright,

341
00:16:45,660 --> 00:16:46,630
let's stop there.

342
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:48,670
Once we're home,

343
00:16:48,790 --> 00:16:50,270
we don't talk about unpleasant things.

344
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:52,370
That's what Hongda and I agreed on.

345
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:54,850
There are plenty of worries,

346
00:16:54,950 --> 00:16:55,590
right?

347
00:16:55,710 --> 00:16:58,150
Everyone needs a place to retreat to.

348
00:16:58,310 --> 00:16:59,590
When we're at home,

349
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:01,290
we talk about happy things.

350
00:17:01,430 --> 00:17:03,550
It helps us relax.

351
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:04,550
Isn't that nice?

352
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:10,109
How do you manage to stay

353
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:12,310
so optimistic no matter what happens?

354
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,550
And so determined?

355
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,550
What's the alternative to being optimistic?

356
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:16,970
Crying every day?

357
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:21,790
We're all

358
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:23,829
really lucky

359
00:17:23,849 --> 00:17:24,710
to have met you two

360
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:26,470
as soon as we joined the company.

361
00:17:29,870 --> 00:17:31,030
I still remember

362
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,880
the first time you came to our house.

363
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:35,280
You said you wanted to help with the chores.

364
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,650
And what happened?

365
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,390
-You broke...
-I broke the pot.

366
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,700
Those were good times.

367
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,630
You young people

368
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:48,010
would come over for dinner every now and then.

369
00:17:48,390 --> 00:17:50,070
We'd talk about art,

370
00:17:50,310 --> 00:17:51,450
and gossip a bit.

371
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:52,580
It was wonderful.

372
00:17:53,390 --> 00:17:54,500
Back then, Hongda

373
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:56,810
wasn't as busy as he is now.

374
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:58,730
But he's the kind of person

375
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:00,240
who can't settle down.

376
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,750
He doesn't want to be ordinary.

377
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:04,540
He says a real man should have ambitions.

378
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:06,150
That's fine too.

379
00:18:07,390 --> 00:18:09,210
Hongda is full of authority.

380
00:18:20,430 --> 00:18:21,180
Um,

381
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,630
is this okay?

382
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:24,910
Do I need to pick these leaves?

383
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:26,570
Let me do it.

384
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:28,320
You're still the same as before,

385
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:29,580
not good at housework.

386
00:18:31,190 --> 00:18:32,950
I really don't have much time

387
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,750
to get involved in this.

388
00:18:36,230 --> 00:18:36,990
I'll go get the door.

389
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:37,610
Alright.

390
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:40,960
Coming.

391
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:42,350
-Madam Zhang.
-Hello.

392
00:18:44,650 --> 00:18:45,660
Ah, Yidi.

393
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:47,180
Come in, come in.

394
00:18:47,710 --> 00:18:48,300
Hello, Chief Editor Xie.

395
00:18:48,330 --> 00:18:49,360
Hello.

396
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:51,880
I came to see you and my mentor.

397
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:53,390
I brought some fruit for you.

398
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:54,810
Your mentor is working overtime.

399
00:18:55,870 --> 00:18:57,710
Well, I'll leave you to it then. I'll be going.

400
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,660
No, don't go.

401
00:18:58,660 --> 00:18:59,470
I'm making dumplings today.

402
00:18:59,630 --> 00:19:00,880
Stay and have some dumplings.

403
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:01,790
You two,

404
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:03,470
clean the celery now.

405
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:04,150
I'll chop the meat.

406
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:06,870
Is it convenient?

407
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:08,030
Is it okay?

408
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,240
It's okay, right?

409
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,150
It's okay.

410
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:11,270
What are you talking about?

411
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,340
Hurry up.

412
00:19:12,470 --> 00:19:13,370
Um,

413
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:14,630
change your shoes.

414
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:16,470
Change your shoes and let's clean the celery together.

415
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:16,950
Okay.

416
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:26,510
Come on.

417
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,650
The dumplings are ready.

418
00:19:28,870 --> 00:19:29,830
They're steaming hot.

419
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:30,770
Come on.

420
00:19:31,140 --> 00:19:32,460
-Hongda is working overtime today.
-It smells good.

421
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,400
He's not coming back for dinner.

422
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,390
It's just the three of us.

423
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:35,630
Let's have a good meal, just the three of us.

424
00:19:35,630 --> 00:19:36,300
Eat, eat, eat.

425
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:37,970
Sorry about that,

426
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:38,510
Hongda.

427
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:40,510
We'll be enjoying this feast without you.

428
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:42,950
How about we have a drink together?

429
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:44,550
I have to drive back.

430
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:46,750
We can get a designated driver.

431
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:47,550
It's decided then.

432
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,260
Let's have a drink.

433
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,640
I happen to have some good wine.

434
00:19:50,070 --> 00:19:50,750
Mrs. Zhang.

435
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:52,310
Are you sure you can handle it?

436
00:19:53,270 --> 00:19:54,270
I'll drink with you till the end.

437
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:55,920
This wine just happens to be here.

438
00:19:56,030 --> 00:19:56,820
I haven't put it away.

439
00:19:56,910 --> 00:19:57,840
Let me, let me, I'll do it.

440
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:02,070
Let's celebrate.

441
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:03,190
Let's celebrate...

442
00:20:03,390 --> 00:20:04,300
Let's celebrate...

443
00:20:05,470 --> 00:20:06,230
Alright.

444
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:09,350
Whatever!

445
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:12,950
Eat up.

446
00:20:13,150 --> 00:20:15,170
Dumplings and wine, the more you drink, the better it gets.

447
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:16,720
You should come over more often in the future.

448
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:17,750
You see, if you don't come,

449
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,720
when I'm alone,

450
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:19,710
it's not much fun.

451
00:20:19,710 --> 00:20:20,790
Next time when you're alone,

452
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,920
just call us.

453
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,250
We'll see if we're free,

454
00:20:23,390 --> 00:20:24,510
and if we are, we'll eat together.

455
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:25,110
Madam Zhang,

456
00:20:25,150 --> 00:20:26,750
if you feel bored,

457
00:20:26,950 --> 00:20:27,870
just call me.

458
00:20:27,990 --> 00:20:29,670
I can come over for a free meal too.

459
00:20:30,430 --> 00:20:30,910
Come on.

460
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:31,510
Come on.

461
00:20:33,970 --> 00:20:35,420
Let's be happy, okay?

462
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:38,140
You finished it?

463
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,590
Didn't I say I'd drink till the end?

464
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:40,880
Your alcohol tolerance is pretty good.

465
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,740
Well, I'll finish mine too.

466
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:43,310
You're all such heroines.

467
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:44,570
I... I can't do it.

468
00:20:45,450 --> 00:20:46,420
I'll just take a sip, just a sip.

469
00:20:46,420 --> 00:20:47,670
Take your time.

470
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:15,710
Well, we'll be going now, Madam Zhang.

471
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:16,590
No, leave them there.

472
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:17,810
I'll organize them myself.

473
00:21:19,370 --> 00:21:20,790
You two take it easy on the road.

474
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,030
Send me a WeChat message when you get there.

475
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:23,620
-I ate too much today.
-Don’t worry.

476
00:21:23,730 --> 00:21:25,330
Don't worry. You can go back now.

477
00:21:25,670 --> 00:21:26,590
Come visit often.

478
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:28,030
You too, you hear me?

479
00:21:28,710 --> 00:21:29,520
Mrs. Zhang.

480
00:21:30,230 --> 00:21:31,070
What is it?

481
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:32,940
Please let us know if anything happens at home, okay?

482
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:35,710
We'll see each other again. You really scared me.

483
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:37,550
The elevator's here.

484
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,590
-We’re leaving.
-Okay.

485
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,470
Bye, Mrs. Zhang.

486
00:21:39,990 --> 00:21:40,400
Bye.

487
00:21:40,630 --> 00:21:41,310
Bye.

488
00:21:42,390 --> 00:21:43,190
I'm so full.

489
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:45,590
I didn't expect

490
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:47,540
to run into her making dumplings today.

491
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:48,880
Because I love eating

492
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,670
those pork and celery dumplings.

493
00:21:51,270 --> 00:21:53,140
They have known this for years.

494
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:54,790
What a coincidence!

495
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:56,590
-I didn’t expect you to come here today...
-Yeah.

496
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:58,310
I was feeling quite embarrassed just now.

497
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:01,100
In a while,

498
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:03,850
if you don't have any plans later,

499
00:22:03,910 --> 00:22:05,070
let's go for a walk.

500
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,300
Sure, I don't have any plans.

501
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:08,130
Alright, it's perfect for digestion.

502
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:11,630
You probably know that

503
00:22:11,630 --> 00:22:13,430
when I first joined Zhongshang Trend,

504
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:14,950
Hongda took me under his wing for news reporting.

505
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:15,950
So in a way,

506
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:17,570
he was like a mentor to me.

507
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:20,090
Moreover, Hongda and his wife are such wonderful people.

508
00:22:20,230 --> 00:22:22,320
They treated everyone in our company like family.

509
00:22:22,470 --> 00:22:23,200
We were all young back then.

510
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,350
None of us were married.

511
00:22:24,430 --> 00:22:25,970
We'd go to their place for meals every day.

512
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:27,190
And Mrs. Zhang was a great cook.

513
00:22:27,190 --> 00:22:28,760
Those guys would eat a lot.

514
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,930
By mid-month, we'd practically eaten them out of house and home.

515
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:32,190
So that's where my mentor

516
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:34,150
got his habit of inviting people over for meals

517
00:22:34,150 --> 00:22:36,110
and treating them to dinner.

518
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,030
I guess so.

519
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:39,030
Later, Hongda left the company, you know,

520
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:39,950
to start his own business.

521
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,830
As for the original group from the company,

522
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,790
some changed careers,

523
00:22:44,790 --> 00:22:46,130
some transferred,

524
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,240
and some got promotions.

525
00:22:47,430 --> 00:22:49,590
In the end,

526
00:22:49,590 --> 00:22:51,230
I think I'm the only one left from the original group,

527
00:22:51,230 --> 00:22:52,710
still at Zhongshang Trend.

528
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:54,790
I can see that

529
00:22:54,910 --> 00:22:57,710
you must have deep feelings for Zhongshang Trend.

530
00:22:57,730 --> 00:22:58,540
Indeed, I do.

531
00:22:58,540 --> 00:22:59,990
I really miss those times.

532
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:01,710
Everyone was so straightforward back then.

533
00:23:01,710 --> 00:23:03,260
we were young,

534
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:05,450
full of ideals and aspirations.

535
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:07,190
And Hongda's home at that time

536
00:23:07,190 --> 00:23:08,270
was like a

537
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:09,520
sanctuary for us.

538
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,550
No matter who had any troubles,

539
00:23:11,630 --> 00:23:13,950
a meal at their place could solve everything.

540
00:23:14,150 --> 00:23:15,330
And over all these years,

541
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:17,320
I've seen so many couples,

542
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:19,630
but I think Hongda and his wife are

543
00:23:19,710 --> 00:23:21,110
the couple with the best relationship.

544
00:23:21,430 --> 00:23:23,670
When you're with them, you feel

545
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:25,500
a special warmth in your heart.

546
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:26,430
Yes,

547
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:27,880
I always say that

548
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:30,230
my mentor is such a warm-hearted guy.

549
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:34,750
I'm really grateful to my mentor.

550
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:37,990
Without him, I probably wouldn't be where I am today.

551
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:40,630
He recruited me into Huake Vision back then,

552
00:23:40,670 --> 00:23:42,670
and then introduced me to various opportunities along the way.

553
00:23:42,910 --> 00:23:44,740
That's how I eventually got into venture capital.

554
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:47,070
So this time,

555
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:49,790
I want to do everything in my power

556
00:23:49,790 --> 00:23:51,030
to help my mentor.

557
00:23:51,710 --> 00:23:54,210
I just hope that good people like my mentor

558
00:23:54,390 --> 00:23:56,190
will definitely be rewarded.

559
00:23:56,190 --> 00:23:57,470
They must have good fortune.

560
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,390
-Actually, I...
-Actually, I...

561
00:24:04,370 --> 00:24:05,390
You go first.

562
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:06,490
I...

