00:24:18,630 --> 00:24:21,460
I didn't investigate thoroughly.

569
00:24:21,590 --> 00:24:23,190
It was an unfounded accusation.

570
00:24:25,230 --> 00:24:26,100
Moreover,

571
00:24:26,950 --> 00:24:28,470
I always thought you were

