573
00:24:30,390 --> 00:24:32,410
But in the past few days, I learned that

574
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:34,340
you've actually been busy

575
00:24:34,340 --> 00:24:36,340
helping with my mentor's affairs,

576
00:24:36,470 --> 00:24:38,110
making connections and offering assistance.

577
00:24:38,870 --> 00:24:40,460
Anyway,

578
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:42,350
I'm the kind of person who

579
00:24:42,550 --> 00:24:43,990
