580
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:45,700
and apologizes for my mistakes.

581
00:24:45,910 --> 00:24:46,680
So,

582
00:24:47,470 --> 00:24:48,410
Ms. Xie,

583
00:24:49,030 --> 00:24:50,690
I'm truly sorry about this matter.

584
00:24:50,790 --> 00:24:52,990
