Also, when I went to the company that day,

597
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,230
my attitude towards you wasn't good either.

598
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,030
With this incident,

599
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,590
you must have suffered a lot of grievances.

600
00:25:17,170 --> 00:25:18,430
But I didn't want to explain,

601
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:19,590
because I felt that explanations

602
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,630
were meaningless.

603
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:21,590
But someday,

604
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:23,390
I will definitely compensate for this.

605
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:24,320
No, no,

606
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:25,390
there's no need for any compensation.

607
00:25:25,500 --> 00:25:26,820
To be honest, I feel

608
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,790
that being able to

609
00:25:28,990 --> 00:25:31,220
speak openly with you like this today

610
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:33,590
makes me quite satisfied and happy.

611
00:25:33,630 --> 00:25:35,270
Don't be so formal with the "Ms." thing.

612
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:36,030
You're being too polite.

613
00:25:36,030 --> 00:25:37,660
You can just call me by my name.

614
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:39,070
That won't do.

615
00:25:39,270 --> 00:25:40,070
That would be too disrespectful.

616
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:41,860
I'll call you Hui, if that's alright.

617
00:25:41,950 --> 00:25:42,510
That's fine,

618
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:44,120
whatever you're comfortable with.

619
00:25:45,630 --> 00:25:47,350
Actually, after getting to know you, I've found that

620
00:25:47,350 --> 00:25:49,070
you're not as intimidating as I thought.

621
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,150
"Intimidating"? That's quite a word to use.

622
00:25:51,330 --> 00:25:53,070
A little, when I first met you.

623
00:25:53,590 --> 00:25:53,990
Yes,

624
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:56,110
I know that sometimes the impression I give

625
00:25:56,190 --> 00:25:58,360
on the surface can be a bit

626
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,960
like a chameleon, I suppose.

627
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:01,140
Perhaps I'm always

628
00:26:01,830 --> 00:26:03,150
changing my appearance

629
00:26:03,150 --> 00:26:04,850
to adapt to various situations in this world.

630
00:26:05,150 --> 00:26:06,100
But no matter what,

631
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:07,350
I still clearly know

632
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:08,430
who I truly am.

633
00:26:08,910 --> 00:26:10,410
I think the same way.

634
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:13,830
I want to protect my original intention in my heart

635
00:26:13,830 --> 00:26:16,460
and then face this indifferent world.

636
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:19,030
I really wish we could be friends.

637
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:21,280
Aren't we already?

638
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:24,670
Then let's properly introduce ourselves.

639
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:26,270
Your friend, Xie Linhui.

640
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,260
Jiang Yidi.

641
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:31,100
Oh, right.

642
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:34,940
Is there anything I can help with regarding that article?

643
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:36,950
I was just about to ask you about that.

644
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:38,310
That day when you went to the agency,

645
00:26:38,310 --> 00:26:40,570
what was that about Xu Delin asking you for money?

646
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:43,370
Well,

647
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:46,790
he told me that's how your agency always does things.

648
00:26:46,950 --> 00:26:48,950
And that money doesn't go into his pocket,

649
00:26:48,950 --> 00:26:49,870
it goes to your agency.

650
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:50,630
How much?

651
00:26:50,740 --> 00:26:51,720
150,000.

652
00:26:53,590 --> 00:26:55,500
Did anyone else from our agency contact you?

653
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:57,450
No, that's all.

654
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,670
So you firmly believed that this money

655
00:26:59,870 --> 00:27:00,990
was requested by me?

656
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:06,470
And other people from your agency

657
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,630
told me the same thing.

658
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:08,550
Who?

659
00:27:09,030 --> 00:27:11,310
The person who escorted me out

660
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:13,630
when I caused a scene that day, called...

661
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,470
Lv Jian?

662
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:15,980
I think so.

663
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:46,750
If you believe that

664
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:48,270
the final draft you reviewed

665
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:50,430
is different from the one published,

666
00:27:50,870 --> 00:27:53,720
you're questioning whether someone

667
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:55,450
in the entire workflow replaced the manuscript.

668
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:57,590
