00:28:19,250 --> 00:28:22,580
[President Li]

672
00:28:35,710 --> 00:28:36,750
President Li.

673
00:28:37,310 --> 00:28:38,410
No, no. It's okay.

674
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:40,920
I'm looking at

675
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,670
