676
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:44,790
Please, go on.

677
00:29:02,430 --> 00:29:03,740
Hello, Hui.

678
00:29:03,990 --> 00:29:04,870
What is it?

679
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:05,910
Jingjing.

680
00:29:05,910 --> 00:29:07,460
Has anyone touched

681
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,740
the draft of the report on Yuxiang Investments

682
00:29:08,740 --> 00:29:10,820
after I reviewed it last time?

683
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,520
No.

684
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:14,930
If anyone accessed it, they would have to sign.

685
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:16,300
I have no record of that.

686
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:22,300
Did Lv Jian touch it?

687
00:29:23,610 --> 00:29:24,830
No.

688
00:29:25,990 --> 00:29:26,950
Hui,

689
00:29:27,150 --> 00:29:29,070
are you suspecting something?

690
00:29:29,390 --> 00:29:30,440
Just asking casually.

691
00:29:33,630 --> 00:29:34,510
Hui,

692
00:29:34,630 --> 00:29:35,720
I heard

693
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:38,170
Mr. Gao asked you to attend a meeting at the group today.

694
00:29:38,510 --> 00:29:39,730
Are you okay?

695
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:41,030
It's nothing.

696
00:29:41,050 --> 00:29:42,180
Don't worry too much.

697
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:43,950
Alright, you go ahead with your work.

698
00:29:44,670 --> 00:29:45,750
I'm hanging up. Bye.

699
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,200
Your approach

700
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:07,570
only sends one message to the outside world:

701
00:30:07,670 --> 00:30:09,950
that Zhongshang Trend is having internal conflicts.

702
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:16,250
If you really

703
00:30:16,270 --> 00:30:18,210
have Zhongshang Trend's best interests at heart,

704
00:30:18,430 --> 00:30:20,400
then find a way to make this matter

705
00:30:20,510 --> 00:30:21,790
blow over as quickly as possible.

706
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:29,390
President Li,

707
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:30,920
rest assured.

708
00:30:31,150 --> 00:30:31,860
I understand.

709
00:30:32,550 --> 00:30:33,210
Alright.

710
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,250
Xie Linhui has been dismissed.

711
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:41,920
That was quick.

712
00:30:42,430 --> 00:30:43,820
Although it's a temporary dismissal,

713
00:30:43,850 --> 00:30:45,330
President Li's intention is

714
00:30:45,430 --> 00:30:47,030
to give Xie Linhui a way out.

715
00:30:49,670 --> 00:30:51,830
This time, she'll never be able to recover.

716
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:56,620
Well, this is

717
00:30:58,070 --> 00:30:59,150
