718
00:31:03,670 --> 00:31:04,870
You're not happy?

719
00:31:05,580 --> 00:31:07,200
I've finally made it.

720
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:09,410
How could that be?

721
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,780
Of course I'm happy.

722
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:15,510
We don't have to sneak around anymore.

723
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:19,090
I'm so sick of it.

724
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:21,350
Having to avoid people every time we go on a date.

725
00:31:21,390 --> 00:31:22,750
It feels like we're having an affair.

726
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,870
About this Xie Linhui matter,

727
00:31:27,430 --> 00:31:28,990
you cooperated so well.

728
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:30,670
You've really done a great service.

729
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:34,480
[[Data Fraud? The Hidden Secrets Behind Wu Yueting's Business Layout]]

730
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:40,510
But,

731
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:43,210
I just feel

732
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:46,190
a bit uneasy inside.

733
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,330
You're silly.

734
00:31:49,470 --> 00:31:50,590
If Xie Linhui doesn't leave,

735
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,990
we'll never have our chance to shine.

736
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,220
