740
00:32:09,430 --> 00:32:10,290
Why not?

741
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:13,230
Didn't you say

742
00:32:13,230 --> 00:32:14,630
that once Xie Linhui left,

743
00:32:14,630 --> 00:32:16,380
you would make our relationship public?

744
00:32:17,430 --> 00:32:18,290
What's wrong?

745
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:19,510
You're having second thoughts, aren't you?

746
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:21,090
Are you having second thoughts?

747
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:23,190
You think I don't want the whole world to know

748
00:32:23,190 --> 00:32:24,510
that you're mine?

749
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:29,430
Think about it, you're Xie Linhui's assistant,

750
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:31,390
and I'm the deputy chief editor of the magazine.

751
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:33,150
