752
00:32:33,150 --> 00:32:35,080
people will definitely think

753
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:36,270
that the previous article

754
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:37,990
was a setup by us.

755
00:32:39,150 --> 00:32:39,870
Besides,

756
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,440
even if Xie Linhui leaves,

757
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:42,910
her informants are still around.

758
00:32:43,430 --> 00:32:45,550
Her roots in the company run so deep,

759
00:32:46,150 --> 00:32:48,550
and her network is so extensive.

760
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:51,170
We can't let all our efforts go to waste.

761
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:53,550
How much longer do we have to wait?

762
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:56,670
My parents have been pressuring us to get married

763
00:32:56,670 --> 00:32:57,740
and buy a house.

764
00:32:57,820 --> 00:32:59,550
You need to give them an answer, don't you?

765
00:33:01,210 --> 00:33:01,830
Also,

766
00:33:01,870 --> 00:33:03,470
I haven't even met your parents yet.

767
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:05,650
Wait,

768
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:07,060
Lv Jian, let me ask you something.

769
00:33:07,870 --> 00:33:10,580
Do you think I'm not good enough to introduce to them or what?

770
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:12,160
Tell me the truth.

771
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:16,180
How did this conversation turn into a real argument?

772
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:17,910
Alright, alright, come here.

773
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:19,510
