785
00:33:47,270 --> 00:33:48,270
We've already waited for two years,

786
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:50,070
what's a little more time?

787
00:33:57,030 --> 00:33:58,190
Okay.

788
00:33:59,830 --> 00:34:01,110
That's my girl.

789
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:24,590
Hello, Mom.

790
00:34:25,030 --> 00:34:25,590
What's wrong?

791
00:34:26,110 --> 00:34:28,120
Uncle Chang has something to tell you.

792
00:34:28,389 --> 00:34:30,020
Be patient and listen carefully.

793
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:38,000
Hui,

794
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:42,000
I ran into Zhang from the Municipal Publicity Department today.

795
00:34:42,190 --> 00:34:43,870
He was asking me about your situation.

796
00:34:45,949 --> 00:34:47,550
Have you gotten into some trouble?

797
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:48,830
No, I haven't.

798
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:50,260
What trouble could I have gotten into?

799
00:34:50,590 --> 00:34:51,310
Uncle Chang,

800
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:53,199
it's just normal work-related matters.

801
00:34:53,230 --> 00:34:54,510
Please don't worry.

802
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:56,030
You're downplaying the seriousness of the situation.

803
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:58,380
I've already inquired about it.

804
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:00,430
That article from your magazine

805
00:35:00,430 --> 00:35:01,810
has caused a dispute.

806
00:35:02,140 --> 00:35:02,750
Hui,

807
00:35:03,350 --> 00:35:04,350
I've always reminded you

808
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:07,650
that a journalist's pen can be a matter of life and death,

809
00:35:07,950 --> 00:35:09,350
can affect vast fortunes,

810
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:11,110
can determine right from wrong,

811
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:13,260
and can make or break reputations.

812
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:16,330
[Hang up]

813
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:16,330
[Chen Chen Chen Nianzhen]

814
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:15,070
As someone with a voice,

815
00:35:15,390 --> 00:35:16,260
you should know

816
00:35:16,390 --> 00:35:18,830
how serious the consequences of abusing that power can be.

817
00:35:19,950 --> 00:35:20,760
This matter

818
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,110
has a significant impact.

819
00:35:22,470 --> 00:35:23,630
You should handle it properly.

820
00:35:24,190 --> 00:35:25,030
Do you understand?

821
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:28,110
Good.

822
00:35:28,250 --> 00:35:29,370
Your mother wants to talk to you.

823
00:35:31,590 --> 00:35:32,480
Hui,

824
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:34,120
Uncle Chang

825
00:35:34,310 --> 00:35:35,910
is also doing this for your own good.

826
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,580
Do you know how anxious he was

827
00:35:37,580 --> 00:35:38,390
after seeing

828
00:35:38,390 --> 00:35:39,670
all that messy information

829
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:41,150
online today?

830
00:35:44,530 --> 00:35:46,680
What's really going on with you?

831
00:35:47,950 --> 00:35:50,000
You're really worrying me.

832
00:35:50,230 --> 00:35:52,310
If Zhongshang Trend is really that bad,

833
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:53,750
didn't I tell you

834
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:55,140
to stop working there?

835
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,430
And also,

836
00:35:57,430 --> 00:35:59,420
that Deputy President position at Liu's publishing house...

837
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,610
You can take it if you like it.

838
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:02,510
If you don't want to do that, then tell me,

839
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:04,110
what do you want to do?

840
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:05,790
-Hello?
-Think about it.

841
00:36:05,790 --> 00:36:07,010
-We can arrange it.
-Hello?

842
00:36:07,270 --> 00:36:09,620
Mom, why can't I hear you clearly anymore?

843
00:36:11,310 --> 00:36:12,060
Hello?

844
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:14,060
I know it's not easy for you,

845
00:36:14,650 --> 00:36:15,830
-But sometimes…
-Hello?

846
00:36:15,830 --> 00:36:17,110
You have to consider the bigger picture.

847
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,670
[Hang up]

848
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,670
[Chen Chen Chen Nianzhen]

849
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:17,760
Hello?

850
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:55,140
I'm home.

851
00:36:56,310 --> 00:36:57,360
What are you holding in your hand?

852
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,300
Something nice.

853
00:37:00,790 --> 00:37:01,880
Haven't you eaten?

854
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:03,310
I have.

855
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:07,620
I bought you

856
00:37:08,390 --> 00:37:09,730
something you wouldn't expect.

857
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:11,030
Here.

858
00:37:13,430 --> 00:37:14,430
It's still warm.

859
00:37:14,430 --> 00:37:14,990
Yes, it is.

860
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:16,590
-Take it.
-What is it?

861
00:37:16,590 --> 00:37:17,350
I'll open it.

862
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:19,870
Tang Yuan in Sweet Rice Wine?

863
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:21,550
Why did you suddenly buy this?

864
00:37:21,550 --> 00:37:23,110
Yeah, I just happened to pass by the store.

865
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:25,110
And then I remembered the first time

866
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:27,140
you took me to eat Tang Yuan in Sweet Rice Wine.

867
00:37:27,270 --> 00:37:27,750
Remember?

868
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:29,540
It was a small shop run by an old lady.

869
00:37:29,990 --> 00:37:31,360
Wait.

870
00:37:31,990 --> 00:37:33,630
Do you remember what you said back then?

871
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:34,290
I don't remember.

872
00:37:34,890 --> 00:37:36,090
You said,

873
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,030
"Tang Yuan in Sweet Rice Wine is soulless

874
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:39,030
without osmanthus."

875
00:37:39,110 --> 00:37:39,750
Right!

876
00:37:39,790 --> 00:37:40,350
You remember now?

877
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:42,550
I felt like something was missing.

878
00:37:42,550 --> 00:37:43,310
You didn't...

879
00:37:43,430 --> 00:37:44,220
Of course I did.

880
00:37:44,870 --> 00:37:46,070
Mr. Zhou, you're impressive.

881
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:49,310
Quick, quick.

882
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:50,990
Add some.

883
00:37:53,390 --> 00:37:54,590
It smells so good.

884
00:37:54,590 --> 00:37:55,110
Okay, okay.

885
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:56,430
More, more.

886
00:37:56,430 --> 00:37:57,230
Aren't you afraid of gaining weight?

887
00:37:57,950 --> 00:37:59,030
You want more?

888
00:38:01,470 --> 00:38:02,310
That's enough.

889
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:03,860
I felt like when I took a sip earlier

890
00:38:03,860 --> 00:38:05,420
something was missing.

891
00:38:07,340 --> 00:38:08,140
Try it.

892
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:12,190
Is it the same taste as before?

893
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:13,550
Yes, that's the taste.

894
00:38:13,670 --> 00:38:14,070
Good.

895
00:38:14,250 --> 00:38:15,230
Enjoy it.

896
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,580
It's so delicious.

897
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:22,310
Sweet and chewy.

898
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:23,870
I'm so happy.

899
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:26,750
I've found that this kind of food in our memories

900
00:38:26,750 --> 00:38:28,270
is really healing, huh?

901
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,070
Of course.

902
00:38:29,650 --> 00:38:30,670
Sweet things

903
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,390
can make people feel happy.

904
00:38:34,850 --> 00:38:36,470
With you, I'm super happy.

905
00:38:41,350 --> 00:38:42,310
Do you want a bite?

906
00:38:42,830 --> 00:38:43,320
Yes.

907
00:38:46,870 --> 00:38:47,910
Is it that taste?

908
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:48,470
Yes.

909
00:38:48,870 --> 00:38:49,710
It is.

910
00:38:49,730 --> 00:38:51,210
One bite takes us back to the past.

911
00:38:53,390 --> 00:38:54,150
It's so delicious.

912
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,300
Zhou Hang, I've been dismissed.

913
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:20,230
Mom.

914
00:40:20,310 --> 00:40:21,500
Little princess.

915
00:40:21,790 --> 00:40:23,350
Are you ready yet?

916
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:27,480
I'm asking if you've gotten ready

917
00:40:27,630 --> 00:40:29,950
for your date today.

918
00:40:32,110 --> 00:40:32,660
I...

919
00:40:33,790 --> 00:40:34,720
Who's my date?

920
00:40:34,950 --> 00:40:35,830
Jiang Yidi.

921
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:38,960
I went to great lengths to ask Mr. Zhao from the building in front.

922
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:41,620
He introduced you to a very nice young man.

923
00:40:41,910 --> 00:40:42,890
He's a graduate student,

924
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:43,910
with a Puhang household registration.

925
00:40:44,510 --> 00:40:46,790
His parents are even from our hometown.

926
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:51,870
Jiang Yidi!

927
00:40:53,870 --> 00:40:55,180
Yes, Mom?

928
00:40:55,350 --> 00:40:56,830
Hurry up, get a move on!

929
00:40:56,950 --> 00:40:57,630
Don't worry, Mom.

930
00:40:57,750 --> 00:40:59,310
I'm getting ready right now.

931
00:41:00,830 --> 00:41:01,710
Bye.

932
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:21,350
Who is it?

933
00:41:33,830 --> 00:41:34,550
Speak up!

934
00:41:34,660 --> 00:41:35,190
What's wrong?

935
00:41:35,350 --> 00:41:35,870
Di.

936
00:41:36,110 --> 00:41:38,060
Help me, I'm in trouble.

937
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:39,050
What's the matter?

938
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:40,720
The new boss is too difficult to deal with.

939
00:41:40,830 --> 00:41:42,620
He wants to see everyone's progress on industry research.

940
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:43,870
He's taking everyone from the Investment Department

941
00:41:43,870 --> 00:41:47,170
into the meeting room one by one to go over detailed industry reports.

942
00:41:47,390 --> 00:41:48,580
And everything mentioned in previous meetings

943
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:49,920
doesn't count anymore.

944
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:51,990
He says he's reviewed the previous meeting minutes.

945
00:41:52,790 --> 00:41:53,940
Then you should

946
00:41:54,230 --> 00:41:55,430
just submit what you have.

947
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:57,330
Don't you have a lot of projects?

948
00:41:57,360 --> 00:41:59,700
I've been doing due diligence before.

949
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:01,870
How could I have time for such detailed industry research?

950
00:42:02,830 --> 00:42:05,630
Why does Yu Shi need to be so detailed?

951
00:42:05,630 --> 00:42:06,830
The investment focus of venture capital

952
00:42:06,830 --> 00:42:08,460
and private equity funds is certainly different

953
00:42:08,460 --> 00:42:10,790
from that of secondary market securities funds.

954
00:42:10,830 --> 00:42:13,030
Yu Shi has worked on Wall Street after all.

955
00:42:13,180 --> 00:42:14,390
Doesn't he know this?

956
00:42:14,990 --> 00:42:17,110
If Yuxiang Investments wants to grow,

957
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:18,350
we should follow Blackstone's path,

958
00:42:18,350 --> 00:42:19,870
dominating both primary and secondary markets,

959
00:42:20,030 --> 00:42:22,140
and approaching it in three stages: early, mid, and late.

960
00:42:22,390 --> 00:42:23,670
Alright, alright, alright.

961
00:42:23,750 --> 00:42:24,260
Okay.

962
00:42:25,660 --> 00:42:26,630
Tell me what you need.

963
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:28,320
Well,

964
00:42:28,390 --> 00:42:30,590
didn't you do an

965
00:42:30,710 --> 00:42:32,430
industry report on the IoT recently?

966
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,350
Could you send it to me to help me out?

967
00:42:36,830 --> 00:42:37,870
Hold on a second.

968
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,350
Did you receive it?

969
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:49,790
Got it, got it.

970
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:50,470
Di.

971
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:52,510
You're still the most reliable in critical moments.

972
00:42:57,730 --> 00:42:59,430
But when are you coming back?

973
00:42:59,470 --> 00:43:00,630
You haven't been at the company lately.

974
00:43:00,630 --> 00:43:02,070
I really miss you, you know.
